        </answer>
      </task>
    </project>
    
    <remark>
      <p>
        The <em>sum</em> of squares has no factorization pattern. In other words, there is no pattern for <m>a^2+b^2</m>. For example, these have <em>no</em> factorization:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <p><m>x^2+1</m></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><m>x^2+9</m></p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><m>4x^2+36</m></p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </remark>
